title: Partnership

partnership.title: Partnership Status
partnership.text: You can apply for partner status in one or several countries. With this application, you can as well add new countries or new products. Your application will be reviewed by a regional manager. Once it is approved,the partner status and corresponding discounts will be available to you.

developer.title: Developer Status
developer.text: If you are a developer, you can apply for registration with your employer. To submit the application, you will need your employer's Partner ID.

reviewed: Your application will soon be reviewed by a regional manager.
text: While your application is under review, now is a good time to learn what you need to do next to obtain the partner status.
